    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "It's easy to forget renegotiation now that it's out of favour, but we probably need to say what happens with the extension during renegotiation.  I prefer a clean-slate approach - the state of the extension doesn't vary based on what was negotiated previously.  That means that the value can change.  If it's important to maintain a certain size limit, the extension needs to be present."
